data.description:
Introducing a stunning 5-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home nestled in the highly sought-after North Bay Elementary School district. This residence is a haven of comfort and style, offering an abundance of natural light that floods the interiors, creating an inviting and warm atmosphere.

Step inside and discover a modern kitchen that combines functionality with elegance, providing the perfect space for culinary enthusiasts. The kitchen is thoughtfully designed for easy cooking, featuring contemporary appliances and ample counter space.

Beyond the kitchen, this home boasts spacious living areas, perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying quality family time.

Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your dream family home.
